  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI notice one of the libraries (remix-solidity) as loadVersion and compile methods that are dependant on events.\r\n\r\nWould it be possible to create a promisifed version of them?\r\n\r\n- **loadVersion** (located [here](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/blob/master/libs/remix-solidity/src/compiler/compiler.ts#L172))\r\n\r\nIt would be nice if this method can return a promise once the compiler version has been loaded.\r\n\r\n- compile (located [here](https://github.com/ethereum/remix-project/blob/master/libs/remix-solidity/src/compiler/compiler.ts#L83)\r\n\r\nIt would be nice if this method can return a promise of CompilationResult.",
